Added ability to resize own location symbol

The user can set the size of the own location symbol from 0% - 400%
of the original size now.

title: Request lastKnownLocation only when starting a ManagerLocationProvider
message:
Request lastKnownLocation only when starting a ManagerLocationProvider

When the GPSLocationProvider was running, we were listening for GPS_EVENT_SATELLITE_STATUS
and send out a new Location whenever that event is received.
The documentation (https://developer.android.com/reference/android/location/GpsStatus.html#GPS_EVENT_SATELLITE_STATUS)
says that this event is sent periodically (like every second), which means that a new Location was broadcasted periodically
and refresh the AlertView/OwnLocationOverlay and stuff periodcally too which consumes alot of cpu power
